posts.post_title: FS/FT: SOLD Doyle wind-up low grade
posts.post_content:
As most T206 collectors know, the Doyle: wind-up card is a scarce common. I  purchased this example at last weekend’s Philly Show (from a respected Net54 member) for [STRIKE]$50[/STRIKE]. When I got home I realized that I already had it in my low-grade set, and in delightfully worse condition than this one.

The card is SOLD. Shipping is $1 PWE.

If you have any questions please email, NO PMs: [url]mpeich12@gmail.com[/url]

Cheers, Mike
